    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver at a lower price point. While the car is mechanically sound and drives well, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. It has been regularly serviced, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. This is a great choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
