      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, swirl marks, or rock chips, further protected by a professionally applied multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory aroma; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, while the high-gloss trim remains scratch-free. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively by authorized technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with the precision of a new vehicle. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, showing no signs of road wear or environmental exposure. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44500.0,
